trans-unit.source: Calculate depreciation according to conditions that you specify. If the related depreciation book is set up to integrate with the general ledger, then the calculated entries are transferred to the fixed asset general ledger journal. Otherwise, the calculated entries are transferred to the fixed asset journal. You can then review the entries and post the journal.

Daca registrul de amortizare aferent este configurat pentru a se integra cu registrul contabil, atunci intrarile calculate sunt transferate in jurnalul registrului contabil al mijloacelor fixe. In caz contrar, inregistrarile calculate sunt transferate in jurnalul mijloacelor fixe. Apoi puteti revizui intrarile si publica jurnalul.
